{
  "stem": "3012.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father, my uncle, my grandmother, my grandfather, the children, and my aunts were are all directed to the left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother, my Aunt Olga, and I were directed to the right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not by Mengele, by a tall, rat-faced high ranking SS man, who turned out to be Heinz, Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Heinz-- some doctor-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Heinz Thilo.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took me 30 years, I believe, 30 years to track him down through the Wiesenthal Center.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I wrote to Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Wiesenthal, and he gave me the news that Thilo committed suicide on the day of the German surrender.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's a hero for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some hero.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually they marched us to the-- I remember the last word of my father telling Mother, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you say [NON-ENGLISH], it means my cherie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] they are separating us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the last time we heard his voice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [CRYING] It's been 51 years, but it's like yesterday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] So they marched us to the-- they, they said we should leave everything there because we will get it back, and we should be very careful how we put everything where so that we don't mess up the order.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took us to the-- oh yeah, they told us they after bath you will get water, and food, and all the nonsense.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we had to leave our clothing there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The shoes sometimes could be retrieved, but there was some fetid looking water that they put the shoes in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of a disinfectant or something, or just part of torture, who knows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you were able to retrieve that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they shaved all our body hair-- but I mean all of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
